title: Hesitate
info:
Lyrics:
What I'm feeling now I can't explain
to throw it all away
lost lonely in the rain
torn up by this incredible pain
then mountains fall apart
I know it's just the start
something there makes me﻿ wait
forever to hesitate.

I lie alone at night
paint pictures in my mind
my mistakes make me blind
my anger my thorn in my side
and still you make me guess
at what I must confess
for us to stop the fight
and you to make it alright.﻿
